Topics

There are hundreds of topics and thousands of variables across all of our surveys. We have 5 main topics which we have listed multiple subtopics that could be found under the main topic, depending on the survey.
Please use this subtopic list to help you find the right subtopic search term to use in the Survey Explorer Search Bar to find the survey that has your topic of concern. Note: some surveys contain more than one primary topic.
